The global Cortical Necrosis market is experiencing steady growth driven by several key factors. One of the primary drivers of market growth is the increasing prevalence of kidney diseases worldwide. With factors such as hypertension, diabetes, and lifestyle choices contributing to the rising incidence of kidney-related conditions, the demand for effective treatments for cortical necrosis is on the rise. This trend is expected to fuel the market expansion as healthcare providers and patients seek advanced solutions to manage and treat cortical necrosis effectively.

